popular. Stack incorporates the Cabal build system.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>AoC 2021 Day 01: Sonar Sweep</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/computer-science/programming-challenges/advent-of-code/2021/src/SonarSweep/</link><pubDate>Fri, 18 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/computer-science/programming-challenges/advent-of-code/2021/src/SonarSweep/</guid><description>&lt;div class="citation" citation-icon-class='fas fa-fw fa-globe' cited-by-count='' is-main=''&gt;
